author: aramirez
msg: New parameter is introduced. It indicates what default stylesheet to use for the generated javadocs if no "stylesheetfile" is specified. The possible values are "maven" or "java". "maven" specifies the use of the default maven javadoc stylesheet while "java" specifies that the default javadoc tool stylesheet will be used
